===Noun===
#''(Zoölogy):'' A [[shark]] of the genus ''[[Sphyrna]]'' or ''[[Zygæna]]'', having the eyes set on projections from the sides of the head, which gives it a hammer shape. The ''Sphyrna zygæna'' is found in the North Atlantic. Called also [[hammer fish]], and [[balance fish]].
#''(Zoölogy):'' A fresh-water fish; the stone-roller in the minnow family [[Cyprinidae]].
#''(Zoölogy):'' An African fruit bat ''[[Hypsignathus monstrosus]]'' -- so called from its large blunt nozzle.